# jolie-jsoup

A [jsoup](https://jsoup.org/) Java library connector for [Jolie](https://jolie-lang.org).

## Installation

`jpm add @jolie-jsoup`

## Usage

See the example in <https://github.com/kicito/jolie-jsoup/blob/main/example/example.ol>.
